title: Rowan Blanchard & Emma Gonzalez Celebrate Pride at Teen Vogue Summit
content: Rowan Blanchard and Emma Gonzalez are celebrating the start of pride month! The 16-year-old A Wrinkle in Time and the 18-year-old MSD student spoke on a panel at the 2018 Teen Vogue Summit on Saturday (June 2) at The New School in New York City.
